      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for. The exterior presents nicely with a clean finish, though you will find some minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is tidy and well-preserved, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
